*Sumnje* su se u njoj pojačale kada je čula tu vest. (Doubts in her increased when she heard that news.)

Ona je imala *sumnju* da će to biti problem. (She had a suspicion that it would be a problem.)

Oni su se suočili sa velikom *sumnjom* da će imati problema. (They were faced with a great doubt that they would have problems.)

Ona nije imala *sumnji* da će joj pomoći. (She had no doubt that they would help her.)

Njegov glas je izazvao *sumnju* u njegovoj porodici. (His voice caused doubt in his family.)